    <textTemplates>
        <name>closedWonOppBody</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;Hello {!User.Name},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lead &quot;{!opportunityRecord.Name}&quot; has exceeded the SLA response time of 24 hours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lead Details:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Owner: {!&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;opportunityRecord&lt;/span&gt;.Owner:User.Name}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Created On: {!&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;opportunityRecord&lt;/span&gt;.CreatedDate}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Lead:&amp;nbsp;{!LeadLink}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please take immediate action to follow up.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thanks,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sales Operations&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <name>oppEmailBody</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hello {!User.Name},

Congratulations! The following Opportunity has been marked as Closed Won.
Opportunity Details:
- Opportunity Name : {!opportunityRecord.Name}
- Owner       : {!opportunityRecord.Owner.Name}
- Amount      : {!opportunityRecord.Amount}
- Close Date    : {!opportunityRecord.CloseDate}
- Account Name   : {!opportunityRecord.Account.Name}
- Stage       : {!opportunityRecord.StageName}
- Opportunity Link : {!oppLink}

Please log in to Salesforce to review and take any necessary follow-up actions.
Thanks,
Sales Operations</text>
    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <name>SLABreachTemplate</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hello {!User.Name},

Lead &quot;{!LeadRecord.Name}&quot; has exceeded the SLA response time of 24 hours.
Lead Details:
- Owner: {!LeadRecord.Owner:User.Name}
- Created On: {!LeadRecord.CreatedDate}
- SLA Target: {!LeadRecord.RES_SLA_Due_Time__c}
- Lead:  {!LeadLink}

Please take immediate action to follow up.
Thanks,
Sales Operations</text>
    </textTemplates>
